{"tid":2066863,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"揭曉，PS5只需6千蚊以內就有一部，你買唔買？","createTime":"2020-06-16T14:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T10:35:55.000Z","uid":213877,"like":22,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8b011db1396b40b85ffa6253c8cb159702bed85e","tid":2066863,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔洗8千蚊，只要6千就有一部，買唔買？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/swxG7D6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FswxG7D6.jpg&h=93f1324c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSONY 就已經公佈了新一代遊戲主機 PlayStation 5 了，並且揭露了其遊戲陣容。在主機與配件的外型公佈後，不少網民將其瘋狂惡搞，可見一眾玩家對於 PS5 的熱烈期待。不過另一樣備受關注的就是 PS5 的售價，而這點官方就還未有公佈了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過概然主機已經正式發佈了，而推出日期亦距離不遠，相信官方亦開始與各銷售通路準備開賣的事宜了。因此，要在網上找到一些蛛絲馬跡並非難事。近日就有人發現了在大型零售商 Play-Asia 與網購平台 Amazon (英國) 上，發現了 PS5 的售價。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在 Play-Asia 上，可見到數位版 PS5 的售價為 699.99 美元 (折合港紙 5,425 元)；而在英國 Amazon 上，發現 PS5 2TB 版本的價錢為 599.99 英鎊 (折合港紙 5,833 元)。而從兩者的價格看來，估計 PS5 的最終售價應該會在 6,000 元樓下。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nSBAsEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnSBAsEb.jpg&h=7693059b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1VQ0Zb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1VQ0Zb.jpg&h=3d7c0af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而這個售價比起當年 PS4 在剛推出時的高出 75%，實在令人意外。此外 DualSense 的手把價格為 79.99 美元，亦較當前 DualShock 4 貴上 20 美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.xfastest.com/58506/sony-ps5-selling-price/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.xfastest.com%2F58506%2Fsony-ps5-selling-price%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=d316af87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.xfastest.com/58506/sony-ps5-selling-price/</a>"},{"pid":"a0eb307887f6e2171bbb1f49f05956da1df8b649","tid":2066863,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"唔洗8000$仲買唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec74964cd2f6ce33263a3e3a960bbb6d43308386","tid":2066863,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"6000內有部啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54e63eba56990ec9446806ed1e891b71c1762ef","tid":2066863,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"PS5公佈既GAME LIST<br />\n請試從下列遊戲找出獨佔大作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGTA Online (R*皇朝千秋萬世！GTA will never die!)<br />\nNBA 2K21 (2K)<br />\nGhostwire: Tokyo (Bethesda集團, 三上廠隻新game)<br />\nDeathloop (Bethesda集團, Dishonored廠)<br />\nGodfall (Gearbox)<br />\nHitman III (IO Interactive)<br />\nDemon's Souls (Bluepoint Games, 美國, remake/remaster)<br />\n<br />\nProject Athia (Square Enix)<br />\nResident Evil Village (卡婊版only one way out(outlast))<br />\nPragmata (卡婊版太空BioShock)<br />\n<br />\nHorizon Frobidden West (第一廠)<br />\nSpiderman Miles Morales (第一廠)<br />\nGran Turismo 7 (第一廠)<br />\nRatchet and Clank Rift Apart (第一廠)<br />\nSackboy: A Big Adventure (獨佔)<br />\nAstro's Playroom (第一廠)<br />\n<br />\nStray (Blue Twelve Studio法國)<br />\nReturnal (Housemarque, 芬蘭)<br />\nDestruction AllStars (Lucid, 英國)<br />\nKena: Bridge of Spirits (Ember Lab)<br />\nGoodbye Volcano High (KO_OP, 加拿大)<br />\nOddworld: Soulstorm (Oddworld Inhabitants, 美國)<br />\nJETT: The Far Shore (Superbrothers+Pine Scented)<br />\nSolar Ash (Heart Machine, 美國)<br />\nLittle Devil Inside (N